thread.title: 'Where is Morgan?': Wolves fans react to Moxey press conference
thread.title_full: 'Where is Morgan?': Wolves fans react to Moxey press conference

title: 'Where is Morgan?': Wolves fans react to Moxey press conference
text:
— Stuart Maynard-Keene (@stuup) October 1, 2015 Moxey referencing Chelsea and City. Why? Most fans know we ain’t gonna be at their level. Stoke and Albion on the other hand…. — Lee O'Connor (@LEE__83_) October 1, 2015 What I learnt from the Jez Moxey press conference #wwfc :0 — Martin Holliday (@martholliday) October 1, 2015 
While some thought it was the wrong man facing the flak: There's nothing I've seen this morning that changes the fact Morgan should have been sitting in front of that media answering questions — game of wolves  (@wolves_ink) October 1, 2015 Amazes me how more people seem to be having a go at Moxey rather then Morgan! #WWFC — Leamington Wolves (@LeamWolves) October 1, 2015 
Plenty disagreed with Moxey's praise of Morgan's stewardship: @OfficialWolves pretty sure we haven't moved forwards from 5-6 years ago regarding the first team...mid table champ side — Dan WWFC clarke (@dc77ww) October 1, 2015 @OfficialWolves 8 years of Morgan, same division as when he got it, odder looking stadium, poorer playing squad?? A success???? #n hh
